---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="S/4HANA Cloud Geçişi">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="relative pt-40 pb-24 bg-surface-container overflow-hidden">
        <div class="max-w-[1920px] mx-auto px-12 md:px-24">
            <div class="text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary font-bold text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">SAP S/4HANA CLOUD</span>
                <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold font-headline text-on-background tracking-tight mb-8">S/4HANA Cloud Geçişi</h1>
                <p class="text-xl text-on-surface-variant font-body leading-relaxed">Tüm iş süreçlerinizi bulut tabanlı tek bir platformda toplayarak maksimum verimlilik ve hız sağlayın.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Grow vs Rise -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-surface">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
                <!-- Grow -->
                <div class="bg-primary text-white p-12 rounded-xl relative overflow-hidden">
                    <span class="absolute top-6 right-6 px-3 py-1 bg-white/20 text-white rounded-full text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest">PUBLIC EDITION</span>
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl mb-6">cloud</span>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold font-headline mb-2">Grow with SAP</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-white/60 mb-6">SAP S/4HANA Cloud Public Edition</p>
                    <p class="text-white/80 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-8">Standart iş süreçlerine uygun, hızlı devreye alınabilir bulut çözümü.</p>
                    <div class="space-y-3">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">bolt</span><span class="text-sm">Hızlı ve kolay ölçeklenebilir</span></div>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">security</span><span class="text-sm">Yüksek güvenlik standartları</span></div>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">update</span><span class="text-sm">Otomatik ve düzenli güncellemeler</span></div>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">savings</span><span class="text-sm">Düşük toplam sahip olma maliyeti</span></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Rise -->
                <div class="bg-on-background text-white p-12 rounded-xl relative overflow-hidden">
                    <span class="absolute top-6 right-6 px-3 py-1 bg-primary-container/20 text-primary-container rounded-full text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest">PRIVATE EDITION</span>
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-container text-4xl mb-6">cloud_done</span>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold font-headline mb-2">Rise with SAP</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-6">SAP S/4HANA Cloud Private Edition</p>
                    <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-8">İşletmenizin özel ihtiyaçlarına göre uyarlanabilir, tam kontrol sağlayan bulut çözümü.</p>
                    <div class="space-y-3 text-slate-300">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-container text-sm">tune</span><span class="text-sm">İhtiyaçlarınıza göre tam özelleştirme</span></div>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-container text-sm">admin_panel_settings</span><span class="text-sm">Yüksek düzeyde veri ve süreç kontrolü</span></div>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-container text-sm">sync</span><span class="text-sm">Mevcut sistemlerle tam uyum</span></div>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-container text-sm">lock</span><span class="text-sm">Özel veri koruma ve güvenlik</span></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="py-20">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-8">
            <div class="bg-primary rounded-md p-12 text-center">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold font-headline text-white mb-4">Hangi Model Size Uygun?</h2>
                <p class="text-white/70 mb-8">Greenfield veya Brownfield yaklaşımıyla S/4HANA geçişinizi planlayalım.</p>
                <a href="/iletisim" class="bg-white text-primary px-8 py-3 rounded-md font-bold hover:bg-surface-container-low transition-colors shadow-lg">Bize Ulaşın</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
